MULTIPLICATION TABLE IN BRAINFUCK
Time Warp Studio Brainfuck Showcase

This program prints a 9x9 multiplication table
Each product is formatted as two characters wide
Single digit results use a space prefix for alignment
Two digit results print tens digit then ones digit

The code uses only the 8 Brainfuck commands
The 8 commands are: right left inc dec output input open close

Strategy for each product value: load the ASCII code
of each decimal digit into the scratch cell and output it
Then a space separator and a newline after each row of nine

Tape layout uses a single cell at position zero
All work happens at cell zero throughout execution

